==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: tiān ruò yŏu qíng tiān yì lăo
===Etymology===
Literally: If Heaven has feelings, Heaven too will become aged.
===Proverb===
'''[[天]][[若]][[有]][[情]][[天]][[亦]][[老]]'''
# Heaven has compassion for those who suffer.
